    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-03-08T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-03-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="1022"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1022">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Woodford</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Sherman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-03-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 8, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 170.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt this
                    day of Department dispatch No. 139, dated February 24, 1898, instructing me, at
                    the request of the Secretary of the Navy, to express to the Spanish Government
                    his high appreciation of the services rendered and honors paid by the Cuban
                    authorities to the officers and men of the U. S. S. <hi rend="italic">Maine</hi>
                    on the occasion of the public funeral of the members of the crew lost in the
                    disaster.</p>
                <p>I have this day addressed an official communication to the Spanish minister of
                    foreign affairs, expressing such appreciation.</p>
                <p>I have, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stewart L. Woodford.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
